<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.1">
<l>tuṟappēṉ allēṉiṉpan tuṟavātu niṉṉuruvam</l>
<l>maṟappē ṉallēṉeṉṟum maṟavātu yāṉulakil</l>
<l>piṟappē ṉākaveṇṇēṉ piṟavāmai peṟṟatuniṉ</l>
<l>tiṟattē ṉātaṉmaiyāl tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I will not renounce [divine] bliss. Not renouncing [that],</l>
<l>I will not forget your beauty ever. [By] not forgetting [you],</l>
<l>I do not think that I will be [re]born in [this] world.</l>
<l>Birthlessness was attained because I am yours,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
